{"tid":1836890,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［藍色經濟圈]喝燉湯抗肺炎","createTime":"2020-01-23T11:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:27:21.000Z","uid":78304,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fdfa2e0c5627bdefe0055221f63f745a36ac2789","tid":1836890,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"中国的病毒必須使用中国人的方法治療，西方治療方法只會水土不服。抱了美國爸爸的大腿卻不能治好，是笑話吧<br />\n<br />\n中華五千年流傳下來的傳統，最牛的是廣東人的燉湯，營養都得以保留，是養生抗肺炎的上品。<br />\n<br />\n只有老司機才知道的中国香港燉湯店 - 燉，一碗燉湯就包含了所有抗肺炎的精華。<br />\n<br />\n有發熱可以去喝一碗清熱潤肺的海底椰麥冬川貝燉瘦肉。<br />\n有咳嗽可以去喝潤肺止咳的蟲草花無花果燉雞。<br />\n全身發疼可以去喝黨蔘北芪燉瘦肉，世上抗肺炎最強的就是党，只要你有党心甚麼病毒党都可以替你治好。<br />\n呼吸不暢順要喝花膠螺片燉雞去潤肺補氣。<br />\n<br />\n666吧？緊記一定要喝熱的，我不會忽悠你的，別打算外帶，冷掉或翻熱功效會大減。<br />\n<br />\n四家分店，趕緊去喝，記得分享給小伙伴<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=10005145&amp;chainName=%E7%87%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Frestaurants%3FchainId%3D10005145%26chainName%3D%25E7%2587%2589&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=8c4fc2bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=10005145&amp;chainName=%E7%87%89</a>"},{"pid":"544a244a79cf1f88c1a1c92ee08bc7f4cbc8288e","tid":1836890,"uid":303450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1aa74ec9897dee1fe53a4783157307dcc1884af","tid":1836890,"uid":271516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"有一家是違規的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498ee3e7bc99465512c047fe9f0057272c0c767d","tid":1836890,"uid":78304,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"d1aa74ec9897dee1fe53a4783157307dcc1884af","tid":1836890,"uid":271516,"like":3,